data.description: Come make this artist's oasis your own beach house!  Located on a corner lot, the 3 bedroom 1 bath home with inside utility room also has a fenced-in back yard with a fire pit.  You can enjoy the morning sun from the bonus sunroom or the breakfast nook. And then enjoy watching the sunset at Snead Island.  Just 5 minutes from Emerson Point Preserve, Blackstone Park, Historic Downtown Palmetto, Safe Harbor Regatta Pointe Marina, and Riverside Boat ramp.  Schedule your showing today and make a day of exploring the Manatee Riverfront and Tampa Bay. Conveniently located to all shopping and restaurants, the Sunshine Skyway, and I75. All measurements are approximate.
